PROMPT 6: What are the required elements of a Stormwater Pollution Prevention Plan (SWPPP)?
======================================================================
RESPONSE:
- Preserve Vegetation/Mark Clearing Limits  
- Establish Construction Access  
- Control Flow Rates  
- Install Sediment Controls  
- Stabilize Soils  
- Protect Slopes  
- Protect Drain Inlets  
- Stabilize Channels and Outlets  
- Control Pollutants  
- Control Dewatering  
- Maintain BMPs  
- Manage the Project  
- Protect Low Impact Development (LID) BMPs  

